body:
Cashier at Meijer was a double mask wearing neck beard.
 He had an anxiety attack over me not wearing a mask. jumped back when my items on the belt got to him, then took a deep breath and frantically scanned my items, when done he instantly jumped back into the next isle glaring at me while I swiped my card.
I taped on the 5sq ft of plexiglass separating us and said: don't worry man, you still have this to protect you.
He balled up his fist and started shaking uncontrollably. My receipt printed,  he stepped back in, about threw it at me. I said thank you,  have a good one. He went from shaking to a wave of relief as I stepped away. ...

Could this all have been avoided if he had this get-up protecting his virginity, I mean from the koof?
